    <item>
      <title>智利中央总统竞争者希望减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/chile-center-right-presidential-contender-wants-business-tax-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利中央总统候选人伊芙琳·马特雷斯（Evelyn Matthei）表示，由于她的竞选活动试图在今年的大选中保持其领先者地位，因此她想将该国的公司税率从27％削减到18％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/chile-center-right-presidential-contender-wants-business-tax-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 15:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的地标支出狂欢赢得议会批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/german-lawmakers-pass-landmark-spending-package-ending-era-of-budget-austerity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国立法者通过了一个具有里程碑意义的支出计划，朝着为国防和基础设施的债务融资付出了数千亿欧元的重大一步，并在预算紧缩的几十年结束时预示着。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/german-lawmakers-pass-landmark-spending-package-ending-era-of-budget-austerity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 15:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
