    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚比索在未经证实的Guevara退出报告中潜入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/colombia-peso-slides-on-reports-finance-minister-stepping-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚的债券和货币周二在未经证实的当地媒体报道中跌倒了，该报告称，该国财政部长迭戈·格瓦拉（Diego Guevara）将在短短三个月的职位上下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/colombia-peso-slides-on-reports-finance-minister-stepping-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 13:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Starmer将英国福利削减了50亿英镑，冒着劳动叛乱的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/starmer-slashes-uk-welfare-bill-as-labour-threatens-rebellion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工党政府表示，它将通过削减福利支出，揭示有争议的改革，从而引起了残疾人运动者的批评，并分裂了基尔·斯塔默（Keir Starmer）的理事会，从而节省数十亿英镑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/starmer-slashes-uk-welfare-bill-as-labour-threatens-rebellion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 12:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
